  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The main objective of this project is to provide life-saving shelter and essential household item assistance to internally displaced persons and host community members in the Centre-Nord region. This IOM project distributes shelter kits and essential household item kits. The project provides life-saving assistance to 5,831 people, including 2,471 women, 2,281 men, 1,079 children, and 583 persons with disabilities.</narrative>
  </description>
